continuum-action-move:
The "Move" action renames pages.

Used in the Continuum skin, on the tabs at the top of the page. See for example {{canonicalurl:Talk:Main_Page|useskin=continuum}}

{{Identical|Move}}

continuum-view-create:
Tab label in the Continuum skin. See for example {{canonicalurl:Foo|useskin=continuum}}

When Visual Editor is enabled, it appears next to {{msg-mw|Visualeditor-ca-createsource}}.

{{Identical|Create}}

continuum-jumptonavigation:
Accessibility link for jumping to the navigation links. Visually hidden by default.

See also
* {{msg-mw|Navigation}}

continuum-jumptosearch:
Accessibility link for jumping to the site search. Visually hidden by default.

See also
* {{msg-mw|Search}}

continuum-feature-limited-width-name:
Heading label for limited width. The title of a list that includes the following items:
* {{msg-mw|continuum-feature-limited-width-1-label}}
* {{msg-mw|continuum-feature-limited-width-0-label}}

continuum-feature-limited-width-0-label:
Label for option to disable limited width. An item in a list that has the title {{msg-mw|Continuum-feature-limited-width-name}} and that includes the following items:
* {{msg-mw|continuum-feature-limited-width-1-label}}
* {{msg-mw|continuum-feature-limited-width-0-label}}

continuum-feature-limited-width-1-label:
Label for option to enable limited width. An item in a list that has the title {{msg-mw|Continuum-feature-limited-width-name}} and that includes the following items:
* {{msg-mw|continuum-feature-limited-width-1-label}}
* {{msg-mw|continuum-feature-limited-width-0-label}}

continuum-feature-custom-font-size-name:
Heading label for font size. The title of a list that includes the following items:
* {{msg-mw|continuum-feature-custom-font-size-0-label}}
* {{msg-mw|continuum-feature-custom-font-size-1-label}}
* {{msg-mw|continuum-feature-custom-font-size-2-label}}

continuum-feature-custom-font-size-0-lab:
Label for small (legacy) font size. An item in a list that has the title {{msg-mw|Continuum-feature-custom-font-size-name}} and that includes the following items:
* {{msg-mw|continuum-feature-custom-font-size-0-label}}
* {{msg-mw|continuum-feature-custom-font-size-1-label}}
* {{msg-mw|continuum-feature-custom-font-size-2-label}}

continuum-feature-custom-font-size-1-lab:
Label for standard font size.  An item in a list that has the title {{msg-mw|Continuum-feature-custom-font-size-name}} and that includes the following items:
* {{msg-mw|continuum-feature-custom-font-size-0-label}}
* {{msg-mw|continuum-feature-custom-font-size-1-label}}
* {{msg-mw|continuum-feature-custom-font-size-2-label}}

continuum-feature-custom-font-size-2-lab:
Label for large font size.  An item in a list that has the title {{msg-mw|Continuum-feature-custom-font-size-name}} and that includes the following items:
* {{msg-mw|continuum-feature-custom-font-size-0-label}}
* {{msg-mw|continuum-feature-custom-font-size-1-label}}
* {{msg-mw|continuum-feature-custom-font-size-2-label}}

skin-theme-name:
Label for setting that allows you to change theme. A title of a list that includes the following items:
* {{msg-mw|skin-theme-os-label}}
* {{msg-mw|skin-theme-day-label}}
* {{msg-mw|skin-theme-night-label}}

skin-theme-day-label:
Label for light theme (standard mode). A title of a list that has the title {{msg-mw|skin-theme-name}}, and that includes the following items:
* {{msg-mw|skin-theme-os-label}}
* {{msg-mw|skin-theme-day-label}}
* {{msg-mw|skin-theme-night-label}}

